snippet.title: Guild Wars 2: End of Dragons Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the fight for Tyria’s future in Guild Wars 2: End of Dragons. Explore the beautiful Canthan continent, travel and fish with your friends in your own personal skiff, unlock nine new elite specializations, and more!

To learn more about Guild Wars 2: End of Dragons and prepurchase the expansion to receive extra bonus items, please visit the official site: https://www.guildwars2.com/en/end-of-dragons/
